@scinoptica
@ztirfhtor
#PID infrastructures do not have to rely on publishers, PID infrastructures do not have to rely on federations. A PID infrastructure does not only have to be #OpenSource but PID registries also have to be #decentralized and run on decentralized open protocols (there is more than just the web). PID infrastructures should be platforms that just assist researchers in how to self-soverignly control their own #PIDs in the most convenient, cheap and green way possible.
We have the technology to do this.
And yes, it's also about trust. But more than evaluating why you should trust others, it can also be quite enlightening to look into solutions that reinforce people's trust in themself. #OpenScience #SSI #DataAutonomy #FDM
